  - esp-20.1.1_20250829 (recommended)
* esp-clang-libs: Standalone Clang shared libraries distribution (optional)
  - esp-20.1.1_20250829 (recommended)
* riscv32-esp-elf: Toolchain for 32-bit RISC-V based on GCC
  - esp-15.2.0_20251204 (recommended, installed)
* esp32ulp-elf: Toolchain for ESP32 ULP coprocessor
  - 2.38_20240113 (recommended, installed)
* cmake: CMake build system (optional)
  - 4.0.3 (recommended)
  - 3.22.1 (supported)
* openocd-esp32: OpenOCD for ESP32
  - v0.12.0-esp32-20260304 (recommended, installed)
